    howToGetThere: `Fly from Kathmandu to Nepalgunj (1 hour), then take a bus or jeep on the Bheri Highway to Khalanga, Jajarkot (approximately 6–8 hours from Surkhet). Alternatively, fly to Surkhet and continue by road. No direct air service to Jajarkot.`,
